{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780130214008,"sessionID":"ses_187f8dff3ffekWTw11vPJPQhfy","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_00_gQYkKQ5e82uK5GPpX4nf9112","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"deep-agent-improvement","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public"},"output":"Found 44093 matches (showing first 100)\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/deepseek/logs/iter-005.out:\n  Line 3: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780130203388,\"sessionID\":\"ses_187f8dff3ffekWTw11vPJPQhfy\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_00_YrP206QlXK6C0LV9Oyjg0121\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: name: deep-agent-improvement\\n3: description: \\\"Evaluator-first bounded agent improvement: 5-dim scoring, dynamic profiling, packet-local candidates, guarded promotion.\\\"\\n4: allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]\\n5: version: 1.9.0.0\\n6: triggers:\\n7:   - deep-agent-improvement\\n8:   - agent improvement loop\\n9:   - bounded agent improvement\\n10:   - 5-dimension scoring\\n11:   - integration scanner\\n12:   - dynamic profiling\\n13:   - model-benchmark mode\\n14:   - benchmark a model or prompt framework\\n15: ---\\n16: \\n17: <!-- Keywords: deep-agent-improvement, deep-agent-improvement, agent-improvement, benchmark-harness, score-candidate, promote-candidate, rollback-candidate -->\\n18: \\n19: # Recursive Agent: Evaluator-First Improvement Orchestrator\\n20: \\n21: Evaluator-first workflow for